  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] grew up in a noble family's manor in the outer country. [PAWN_possessive] early years were full of lessons in horseback riding, politics, and religion.\n\n[PAWN_nameDef] and [PAWN_possessive] friends found many ways to break the rules and have fun in the fields and forests. -->
  <CountryLordling92.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]在外地的一個貴族莊園中長大。[PAWN_possessive]早年充滿了騎馬、政治和宗教方面的課程。\n\n[PAWN_nameDef]和[PAWN_possessive]朋友發現了許多打破規則的方法，並在田野和森林中玩樂。</CountryLordling92.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: country lordling -->
  <CountryLordling92.title>田野領主</CountryLordling92.title>
  <!-- EN: country lady -->
  <CountryLordling92.titleFemale>田野領主</CountryLordling92.titleFemale>
  <!-- EN: field lord -->
  <CountryLordling92.titleShort>田野領主</CountryLordling92.titleShort>
  <!-- EN: field lady -->
  <CountryLordling92.titleShortFemale>田野領主</CountryLordling92.titleShortFemale>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef]'s parents did not want another heir. Fearing a succession fight, they decided to neutralize [PAWN_objective] early.\n\nThey pampered [PAWN_nameDef] from birth, preventing [PAWN_objective] from developing the grit or knowledge necessary to be a threat to their favored son. [PAWN_nameDef] learned little more than how to manipulate the royal staff to get more food. -->
  <PamperedLordling37.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]的父母本來不想要另一個繼承人。由於擔心繼位之爭，他們決定儘早讓[PAWN_objective]變得中立。\n\n他們從出生起就寵愛[PAWN_nameDef]，防止[PAWN_objective]培養出對他們寵愛的兒子構成威脅所需的勇氣或知識。[PAWN_nameDef]只學到瞭如何操縱皇室職員以獲得更多食物。</PamperedLordling37.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: pampered lordling -->
  <PamperedLordling37.title>嬌生慣養的領主</PamperedLordling37.title>
  <!-- EN: pampered princess -->
  <PamperedLordling37.titleFemale>嬌生慣養的領主</PamperedLordling37.titleFemale>
  <!-- EN: pampered -->
  <PamperedLordling37.titleShort>嬌生慣養的領主</PamperedLordling37.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef]'s family held their power base on a grand, ancient starship. Born and raised on the ship, [PAWN_nameDef] learned all about the rigors of shipboard life, and the politics and methods of interstellar battle and orbital invasion.\n\n[PAWN_pronoun] learned to feel most at home with strong walls close on all sides and the gentle hiss of atmosphere regulators. -->
  <ShipboundLordling12.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]的家族將他們的權力基地建立在一艘宏偉而古老的星際飛船上。[PAWN_nameDef]在船上出生和長大，學習了嚴酷的船上生活，以及處理星際爭鬥和軌道入侵的政治和方法。\n\n[PAWN_pronoun]認為四面八方的堅固牆壁和大氣調節器的柔和嘶嘶聲最有賓至如歸的感覺。</ShipboundLordling12.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: shipbound lordling -->
  <ShipboundLordling12.title>星艦領主</ShipboundLordling12.title>
  <!-- EN: shipbound lady -->
  <ShipboundLordling12.titleFemale>星艦領主</ShipboundLordling12.titleFemale>
  <!-- EN: ship lord -->
  <ShipboundLordling12.titleShort>星艦領主</ShipboundLordling12.titleShort>
  <!-- EN: ship lady -->
  <ShipboundLordling12.titleShortFemale>星艦領主</ShipboundLordling12.titleShortFemale>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef]'s noble family did not want [PAWN_objective], but could not afford to be seen directly assassinating [PAWN_objective] either. They attempted to get [PAWN_objective] killed by assigning [PAWN_objective] dangerous training without proper protection at too young an age.\n\nAgainst all odds, [PAWN_nameDef] survived the jousting contests, horsewar matches, riverrun competitions and warzones. In the end, it only made [PAWN_objective] stronger. -->
  <UnwantedSurvivor67.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]的貴族本來不想要[PAWN_objective]，但也不能被發現直接刺殺[PAWN_objective]。他們試圖通過在[PAWN_objective]過於年輕的時候，在沒有適當保護的情況下就進行危險訓練來間接殺死[PAWN_objective]。\n\n儘管困難重重，[PAWN_nameDef]在騎槍比賽、馬術比賽、河流競賽和戰區中倖存下來。最後，所有事只會讓[PAWN_objective]變得更強大。</UnwantedSurvivor67.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: unwanted survivor -->
  <UnwantedSurvivor67.title>被棄的倖存者</UnwantedSurvivor67.title>
  <!-- EN: survivor -->
  <UnwantedSurvivor67.titleShort>倖存者</UnwantedSurvivor67.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] was born to a royal house with a grand manor in a great city. [PAWN_pronoun] spent [PAWN_possessive] youth in lessons on politics.\n\nWhenever [PAWN_pronoun] could, [PAWN_pronoun] would escape with [PAWN_possessive] friends to explore the half-built substructure of the metropolis. -->
  <UrbanLordling82.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]出生在一座大城市中擁有宏偉莊園的皇室。[PAWN_pronoun]在政治課上度過了[PAWN_possessive]的青春。\n\n只要[PAWN_pronoun]有機會，[PAWN_pronoun]就會和[PAWN_possessive]朋友一起逃離，探索這座大都市半建成的地下結構。</UrbanLordling82.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: urban lordling -->
  <UrbanLordling82.title>城市領主</UrbanLordling82.title>
  <!-- EN: urban lady -->
  <UrbanLordling82.titleFemale>城市領主</UrbanLordling82.titleFemale>
  <!-- EN: city lord -->
  <UrbanLordling82.titleShort>城市領主</UrbanLordling82.titleShort>
